---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="footer-gradient py-12 mt-12 text-sm relative overflow-hidden">
	<div class="footer-top-border"></div>
	<div class="footer-glow-dot footer-glow-dot-1"></div>
	<div class="footer-glow-dot footer-glow-dot-2"></div>
	<div class="footer-glow-dot footer-glow-dot-3"></div>
	<div class="max-w-[960px] mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
			<!-- Column 1: Site Info -->
			<div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
					<img src="/images/logo-icon.png" alt="" class="w-6 h-6 rounded" />
					<span class="font-bold text-white text-base">AI比較ラボ</span>
				</div>
				<p class="text-blue-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0">
					最新のAIツールを実際に使って比較・レビュー。あなたの用途に合ったベストなAIツールが見つかります。
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Column 2: Navigation -->
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-white font-bold text-sm mb-3 tracking-wide">ナビゲーション</h3>
				<ul class="list-none p-0 m-0 space-y-2">
					<li><a href="/" class="text-blue-100/90 hover:text-blue-100 no-underline transition text-sm">ホーム</a></li>
					<li><a href="/blog" class="text-blue-100/90 hover:text-blue-100 no-underline transition text-sm">記事一覧</a></li>
					<li><a href="/about" class="text-blue-100/90 hover:text-blue-100 no-underline transition text-sm">サイト概要</a></li>
					<li><a href="/contact" class="text-blue-100/90 hover:text-blue-100 no-underline transition text-sm">お問い合わせ</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Column 3: About & Legal -->
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-white font-bold text-sm mb-3 tracking-wide">About AI比較ラボ</h3>
				<p class="text-blue-100/80 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0 mb-3">
					ChatGPT、Claude、Gemini、画像生成AIなど、話題のAIツールを独自の視点で比較します。
				</p>
				<ul class="list-none p-0 m-0 space-y-2">
					<li><a href="/privacy" class="text-blue-100/90 hover:text-blue-100 no-underline transition text-sm">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
					<li><a href="/terms" class="text-blue-100/90 hover:text-blue-100 no-underline transition text-sm">利用規約</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="border-t border-blue-100/20 pt-6 text-center">
			<p class="m-0 text-blue-100/70">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} AI比較ラボ All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.footer-gradient {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #334155 100%);
	}
	.footer-top-border {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, #3b82f6 30%, transparent 50%, #3b82f6 70%, transparent 100%);
	}
	.footer-glow-dot {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.footer-glow-dot-1 {
		width: 120px;
		height: 120px;
		top: 20%;
		left: 5%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
	}
	.footer-glow-dot-2 {
		width: 80px;
		height: 80px;
		top: 60%;
		right: 10%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
	}
	.footer-glow-dot-3 {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		bottom: 10%;
		left: 40%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
	}
</style>
